                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d887">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Pera</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-12-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 29, 1896</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Thirty-five naturalized Americans or the wives and children of such are on ship
                    from Harpoot to America. Nine revolutionists released from Aleppo left
                    Alexandretta last night on ship for Marseilles. Diradourian leaves for America
                    to-day on assurances from palace of security. Have requested withdrawal of guard
                    from Robert College.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Terrell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
